text: "I See Me" is a song recorded by American country music artist Travis Tritt. It was released in March 2005 as the third single from the album My Honky Tonk History. The song reached #32 on the Billboard Hot Country Singles & Tracks chart. The song was written by Casey Beathard and former NFL player Chris Mohr. ==Chart performance== {|class="wikitable sortable" !align="left"|Chart (2005) !align="center"|Peak position |- |} ==References== Category:2005 singles Category:2004 songs Category:Travis Tritt songs Category:Songs written by Casey Beathard Category:Song recordings produced by Billy Joe Walker Jr. Category:Columbia Records singles
